languages.text: "Для чего тебе нужны были провидцы? Зачем так рисковать?"
"What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"
languages.original_text: "Для чего тебе нужны были провидцы? Зачем так рисковать?"

"What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"
"What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"

languages.text: “你为什么要绑架那些先知？为什么要冒这个险？”
languages.original_text: "What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"

traits.locale_text: “你为什么要绑架那些先知？为什么要冒这个险？”

languages.text: « À quoi vous ont servi les Grands Prophètes ? Pourquoi prendre un tel risque ? »
languages.original_text: "What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"

traits.locale_text: « À quoi vous ont servi les Grands Prophètes ? Pourquoi prendre un tel risque ? »

languages.text: «¿Para qué necesitabas a los videntes? ¿Por qué correr semejante riesgo?».
languages.original_text: "What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Para qué necesitabas a los videntes? ¿Por qué correr semejante riesgo?».

languages.text: 「先見司に何の用がある？なぜそんなリスクを冒す？」
languages.original_text: "What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"

traits.locale_text: 「先見司に何の用がある？なぜそんなリスクを冒す？」

languages.text: "Wofür habt Ihr die Runenpropheten gebraucht? Warum ein solches Risiko eingehen?"
languages.original_text: "What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"

traits.locale_text: "Wofür habt Ihr die Runenpropheten gebraucht? Warum ein solches Risiko eingehen?"

languages.text: "Ötesezenlere neden ihtiyacın vardı? Neden bu kadar büyük bir risk aldın?"
languages.original_text: "What did you need the Farseers for? Why take such a risk?"
